{"tid":1266821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[WECONNECT]浩氣長存-勇武和理非-抗惡意志永不滅","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T06:13:23.000Z","uid":265305,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3699bc4ef50ee713753bf3648699f41bab783b","tid":1266821,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"首先 對三位烈士既離去 深切表示哀悼<br />\n你地既遺志 所有香港人都會替你行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n其他話想既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地唔捨得你 留返啲力 簡和理非或勇武派 加入去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幾次活動 69既100萬人<br />\n612既衝擊 加上 615 成就616 既200萬+1<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">期後關注既人 減少左幾多？</span></span>就係因為政府冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為629 71會多返啲人出黎 呢班人有哀悼 更多係影相打卡既師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而呢班人 都會有616為左學生企出黎既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  71過後 班人又會消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為和理非我一直覺得 勇武可以諗清楚再行動 起碼少啲學生受死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係 大家一直以為612半年後佢先會拉人 原來呢幾日已經搜捕緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">630 71 發夢勇武派請隨意發揮<br />\n廢青廢中會用資金買物資補給<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n和理非係你既後盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港豬71出黎行拎人性既光環好和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地放幾多keroro同美少女戰士 夢入面i dont fucking care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n612有經過金鐘都要拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 咁71有出黎遊行都要拉啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n後續文宣 挽回民意  廢青廢中和理非為你努力做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你有你地做 我地為你地做靚個門面佢</span></span><br />\n真正不分化、不督灰、不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nCCTVB毫不尊重烈士 反紅媒遊行 事在必行<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 但請63071勿推撞記者  鏡頭等等</span></span><br />\n發夢點係隔離屌9佢 請食狗糧 言語欺凌呀心靈虐待呀乜乜柒柒呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\">要學識香港韓國學校優良文化</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每一次衝擊都有更多港豬出黎行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba040d9724b86848bb51bcf27051ebfa38b1c26","tid":1266821,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3ed947298f734b8fef2dfd87729d4058e7688299","tid":1266821,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6bd27da141f4c76f0f4c2e9ea5dc59e78fbef7b","tid":1266821,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep